title: Let Them Theory - Comparison
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Comparison is an attempt to control how you rank in the world. "Let Them" breaks this cycle.

* '''Torture vs. Teacher Comparison''':
** ''Torture'': Comparing things you can't change (height, family wealth). Fix: "Let them have that advantage."
** ''Teacher'': Comparing skills/habits you can work toward. Fix: "Let them be proof that it is possible."
* '''Jealousy as a Compass''': Jealousy is data from your future self showing what you value. 
* '''Destroy the Checklist''': Let others follow the societal timeline. Let them think you are "behind" while you run your own race.